Title: Affine Toda Solitons and Systems of Calogero-Moser Type

Authors: H. W. Braden and Andrew N. W. Hone

Comments: 11 pages Latex2e. Some typos corrected

SystemsJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B380 (1996) 296-302

The solitons of affine Toda field theory are related to the spin-generalisedRuijsenaars-Schneider (or relativistic Calogero-Moser) models. This providesthe sought after extension of the correspondence between the sine-Gordonsolitons and the Ruijsenaars-Schneider model.